<h2 id="toc18"><span>MTF ω-0 Roster</span></h2>
<p>The following personnel are possible candidates for Mobile Task Force Omega-Zero (&quot;Ará Orún&quot;).<br />
<strong>Requirements:</strong> Candidates must:</p>
<ul>
<li>Be Foundation personnel (including researchers, field agents, and task force operators but typically not D-Class<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-4" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-4')">4</a></sup>.</li>
<li><em>Have died</em> in a previous work on the wiki.</li>
<li>Deaths should be roughly in the period from 1976 to 2018, but some fudging around the borders is possible.</li>
<li>For developed characters (e.g. not one-off MTF operator red-shirts who died in logs), their creator needs to be available for contact, as I feel that character death is often something that author's have strong feelings of artistic integrity about, and I chose to respect that.</li>
</ul>
<p>Feel free to suggest additional candidates in <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-2241728/mtf-omega-zero-now-recruiting">this thread</a>. I'm especially interested in <em>less</em> interesting candidates at this time: redshirt MTF operatives, Foundation maintenance staff that were in the wrong place at the wrong time, ect. <em>and</em> candidates who died before 2000.</p>
